{"tid":1724061,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［國際戰線］我想大家多謝下烏克蘭人","createTime":"2019-11-15T11:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T19:50:49.000Z","uid":200179,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0d1709ed1fa19590e5c9e392ebb9a7a83f8fb2f1","tid":1724061,"uid":200179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:04:24.000Z","msg":"有個烏克蘭fb page叫Free Hong Kong Center<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ufhkc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fufhkc%2F&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0CvrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=acdc4a0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ufhkc/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5t3sDNB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5t3sDNB.jpg&h=ee48e2ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見到佢哋好支持香港人 當我哋係同鄉咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過冇乜人留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋真係有做野幫助香港民主進程<br />\n關心程度仲高過一般香港人（淨係喺ig講好嬲個啲,no offence真係冇咩用）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/15/185607_dfbc38dbe63a3ad76c2a7c46e8c6e912.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F15%2F185607_dfbc38dbe63a3ad76c2a7c46e8c6e912.jpeg&h=3ee15a50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想大家喺大型和理非活動多謝佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話畀佢哋聽香港人收到佢哋嘅心意，希望同烏克蘭人一齊追求民主自由，繼續幫香港人喺歐洲發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入去個fb page可以了解更多<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ufhkc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fufhkc%2F&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0CvrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=acdc4a0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ufhkc/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KJansJm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKJansJm.jpg&h=70941078&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d9a595aa49b568723d2cff6774b78be6304a745","tid":1724061,"uid":200179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:30:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"82efcd68d409ef792dbc1673782c707d78150c2b","tid":1724061,"uid":200179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:28:39.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d790ce687cada462ee77992c4849cace7789240","tid":1724061,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:33:16.000Z","msg":"Help push"},{"pid":"9b248a25ad9dc1d24a1c228dcd882a6d881b0b7f","tid":1724061,"uid":200179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:59:35.000Z","msg":"係咪要貼烏妹先有人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50cd59b4b766c189565c33058d13acb9d3d16e15","tid":1724061,"uid":200179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"推 入link望下please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d461dbb6cc9928fcc4534cfc88d97f51c47a62","tid":1724061,"uid":200179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:50:24.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a02484b754a8e7be64e2636bcb2c8633d702c20a","tid":1724061,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dffbf060ba7849f711b4ce6523803f86bc0a8c8f","tid":1724061,"uid":120757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-1